/><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa5c7791b716556d2fc538e4695fde9de1cda78","tid":1394024,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:08:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3fd5c5b58094db058ba7b1d18014d17e9705e3b","tid":1394024,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"推比公務員睇"},{"pid":"06cb6fbc8782a1fa49b4049882cb9b4c58beb811","tid":1394024,"uid":258313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:09:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"410cf3ab56f1f4d25892deb29d3534ac83638057","tid":1394024,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:10:55.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年之前落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年之前！"},{"pid":"ccd9349c64ca6f4258a522c607854b802931f1b6","tid":1394024,"uid":254860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:17:01.000Z","msg":"五大訴求! <br />\n光復香港 時代革命!"},{"pid":"837fc29a5c2133a09ac1432ede5dc719752448f0","tid":1394024,"uid":83518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:18:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"180b35fae14c0ffb61aaa3d94be4e03146c0d562","tid":1394024,"uid":281533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:18:51.000Z","msg":"我哋做啱咗"},{"pid":"0ff42e9201172b252d22dd526c8f70ac9db858f7","tid":1394024,"uid":109437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:19:36.000Z","msg":"好彩我唔係警務處人員<br />\n邊個署敢搞人嘅話我可以宣布邊個署就會消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d6fe37b5af9fa3025c23c4cd8231aa47f60b9b","tid":1394024,"uid":78695,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/p6SPF3E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fp6SPF3E.gif&h=6818fdd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d82500aaa4f3c623a82a22c69ed4e81e3e53b933","tid":1394024,"uid":178364,"l